PathOfBuilding.Notes:
General Tips
Levels 1 to 28 Use Frost Blades or Perforate
Frost Blades - purchase from Nessa as soon as you enter A1 town Onslaught Support - After Mercy Mission Ancestral Call - After Mercy Mission GGR
Perforate - reward from Tarkleigh as soon as you enter A1 town Onslaught Support - After Mercy Mission Chance to Bleed - Starter Support for Duelist / Buy on Zerker
For Frost Blades you will want to run Double Strike supported by at least Chance to Bleed for single target.
After Breaking some eggs add: Dash Ancestral Protector - eventually add Maim when you have links Warbanner
After Brutus Leap Slam - Likely drop all Quicksilver flasks for Mana flasks, I like to use 2-3
A2 Add faster attacks to leap slam Blood rage Herald of Purity Flesh and Stone
A3 You can swap Herald of Purity and War Banner out for Pride if you want Take Vulnerability Curse as well
At Level 28 you'll unlock Bladestorm, links are: Bladestorm(r) Rage (r) Close Combat (g) Melee Physical damage (r) Onslaught (g) - if you have GGRR instead of RRRG
Use this til maps then you can switch to cyclone if you want Fortify can be a good 5th Link when you find a 5L
If you need more help swing by my channel at twitch.tv/donthecrown
